description: WisdomTree Long USD Short EUR 5x Daily is designed to provide investors with a 'leveraged long' exposure to US Dollars (USD) relative to Euro (EUR) by tracking the MSFX 5x Long US Dollar/Euro Index(TR) (the Index), which aims to reflect five times the performance of a position in forward contracts which are rolled on a daily basis.
name: WisdomTree Long USD Short EUR 5x Daily
